♪ Kids ruin everything ♪

21:00.427 --> 21:02.095
♪ I almost sleep in their head ♪

21:02.179 --> 21:05.349
♪ I got kids in my head ♪

21:05.432 --> 21:11.396
♪ I never knew but now I see
children ruin everything ♪

21:13.273 --> 21:14.691
♪ Everything ♪

